POLU.SOA
Struct Of Arrays version of the polu application.

Designed for memory usage comparison with the POLU.AOS application.

Derivatives for performance evaluation:
* PAPI      root application for the performance tests
* BRINS     singleton test: number of branch instructions
* FPINS     singleton test: number of floating-point instructions
* LDINS     singleton test: number of load instructions
* SRINS     singleton test: number of store instructions
* TOTINS    singleton test: total number of instructions
* VECINS    singleton test: number of vector instructions
* FLOPS     singleton test: number of floating point operations
